# This directory holds the published crosswalk artifacts:
#   kr_corp_ids.parquet   — machine-readable (pandas/DuckDB)
#   kr_corp_ids.csv       — human-readable; the citable public artifact
#
# Run `python src/build_crosswalk.py` to generate them.
# Once generated, both files are committed to the repo so users can
# access them with a plain `git clone` — no Python or API key required.
